1
00:02:23,410 --> 00:02:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Second Law of Thermodynamics:</i></font>

2
00:02:25,770 --> 00:02:28,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Heat can never pass from 
a colder to a warmer body</i></font>

3
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>without causing other effects,</i></font>

4
00:02:31,270 --> 00:02:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>or it is impossible to convert heat 
from a single source into work</i></font>

5
00:02:35,010 --> 00:02:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>without causing other effects,</i></font>

6
00:02:37,930 --> 00:02:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>or entropy always increases in 
an irreversible heat reaction.</i></font>

7
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Escaping the burden of an entropy increase</i></font>

8
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and to create something from nothing...</i></font>

9
00:02:48,330 --> 00:02:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The witch's power is truly convenient.</i></font>

10
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enter.</font>

11
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Your Highness.</font>

12
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov.</font>

13
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you do what I asked?</font>

14
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's done, Your Highness.</font>

15
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The witch was hanged at noon.</font>

16
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The prisoner wore a hood,</font>

17
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so no one noticed anything unusual.</font>

18
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, very good.</font>

19
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next, prepare some data for me.</font>

20
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. What do you need?</font>

21
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need a report summarizing 
Border Town's trade,</font>

22
00:03:22,110 --> 00:03:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">taxes, and fixed expenditures 
for the past decade.</font>

23
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, let me think...</font>

24
00:03:28,330 --> 00:03:30,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the workshops in the town,</font>

25
00:03:30,850 --> 00:03:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">such as ironworks, textiles, and pottery,</font>

26
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">compile statistics on 
their numbers and scale,</font>

27
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and give me a detailed report.</font>

28
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Include the population distribution and</font>

29
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">occupations in Border Town.</font>

30
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness,</font>

31
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what do you need those for?</font>

32
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. Just give them to me.</font>

33
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

34
00:03:47,370 --> 00:03:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, are you finally 
taking the Royal Decree seriously?</font>

35
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Royal Decree?</font>

36
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:02,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}COLDWIND RIDGE</font>

37
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gerald commands the military 
stronghold of Coldwind Ridge.</font>

38
00:04:04,290 --> 00:04:05,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}VALENCIA</font>

39
00:04:04,290 --> 00:04:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Timothy oversees the 
economic hub of Valencia.</font>

40
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:08,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}PORT OF CLEARWATER</font>

41
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Garcia controls the trade port, 
Port of Clearwater.</font>

42
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}SILVER CITY</font>

43
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tilly operates the cultural 
center of Silver City.</font>

44
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:16,600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}BORDER TOWN</font>

45
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've been banished to 
this desolate Border Town.</font>

46
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, under these circumstances,</font>

47
00:04:19,330 --> 00:04:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what do you think my 
chances of winning are?</font>

48
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. You can be honest.</font>

49
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, each of Their Highnesses' domains 
have their own strengths.</font>

50
00:04:28,650 --> 00:04:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In comparison, it would be very difficult 
to achieve anything in Border Town.</font>

51
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Furthermore, considering 
Your Highness's past performance</font>

52
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and standing among 
the nobles in the capital,</font>

53
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's hard to see any real advantage.</font>

54
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

55
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I need to find 
another way to impress Father.</font>

56
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, let me ask you this:</font>

57
00:04:51,350 --> 00:04:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who truly rules this kingdom?</font>

58
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:54,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course it is</font>

59
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Royal House of Graycastle, 
the Wimbledons, Your Highness.</font>

60
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just an illusion.</font>

61
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The true rulers of this kingdom 
are not in Graycastle,</font>

62
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:04,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}THE ROYAL CAPITAL, GRAYCASTLE</font>

63
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but here.</font>

64
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}THE HOLY CITY, HERMES</font>

65
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Holy City, Hermes.</font>

66
00:05:10,020 --> 00:05:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only those crowned by the Pope 
were considered legitimate kings,</font>

67
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then this secular regime is nothing 
more than a puppet of theocracy.</font>

68
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how prosperously 
my siblings govern their domains,</font>

69
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they ultimately belong to the Church.</font>

70
00:05:22,350 --> 00:05:25,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I can create a kingdom that 
is not bound by the Church,</font>

71
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then the throne will surely be mine.</font>

72
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, you've always been a loyal 
supporter of the Royal House.</font>

73
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't stand the Church's excessive 
interference in secular governance, right?</font>

74
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right,</font>

75
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the Church's power 
is deeply entrenched,</font>

76
00:05:41,130 --> 00:05:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it has the people's support.</font>

77
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What can we do?</font>

78
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The people's support for the 
Church originates from its lies.</font>

79
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can prove the Church is lying,</font>

80
00:05:49,790 --> 00:05:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they will no longer support it.</font>

81
00:05:52,340 --> 00:05:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, witches aren't actually 
the embodiment of the Devil.</font>

82
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's why you saved that witch.</font>

83
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, you've been the Assistant Minister 
of Finance for twenty years, right?</font>

84
00:06:03,530 --> 00:06:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

85
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I win the Royal Decree, 
the "Assistant" in your title can be dropped.</font>

86
00:06:09,180 --> 00:06:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or possibly even further. For example,</font>

87
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Hand of the King."</font>

88
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov,</font>

89
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do not question my decisions.</font>

90
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did His Highness say?</font>

91
00:06:29,790 --> 00:06:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

92
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov!</font>

93
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you even try to talk 
some sense into him?</font>

94
00:06:36,670 --> 00:06:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even listening to me?</font>

95
00:06:38,010 --> 00:06:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's off about this witch business.</font>

96
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just this witch business.</font>

97
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something wrong with 
His Highness Roland himself.</font>

98
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, something's wrong.</font>

99
00:06:46,130 --> 00:06:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is serious.</font>

100
00:06:47,610 --> 00:06:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the news leaks 
and Hermes finds out,</font>

101
00:06:49,990 --> 00:06:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll be in big trouble.</font>

102
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't leave!
Explain yourself!</font>

103
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contract?</font>

104
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand.</font>

105
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an agreement.</font>

106
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you sign the last page,</font>

107
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you and His Highness will be in 
an equal employment relationship.</font>

108
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Equal... employment?</font>

109
00:07:21,990 --> 00:07:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. His Highness specifically 
emphasized this point: equal.</font>

110
00:07:26,090 --> 00:07:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do work.</font>

111
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness pays you 
one gold royal per month.</font>

112
00:07:33,670 --> 00:07:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's... more than what 
my father earns in a year.</font>

113
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there a mistake?</font>

114
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:43,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your pay was set by 
His Highness Roland himself.</font>

115
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:44,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no mistake.</font>

116
00:07:44,450 --> 00:07:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then... what does the prince...</i></font>

117
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>want me to do?</i></font>

118
00:07:50,610 --> 00:07:52,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone like me?</i></font>

119
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna.</font>

120
00:08:04,810 --> 00:08:07,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you? 
Did you sleep well last night?</font>

121
00:08:07,050 --> 00:08:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, very well.</font>

122
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great.</font>

123
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After everything you've gone through,</font>

124
00:08:12,010 --> 00:08:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should've rested longer, 
but we don't have much time.</font>

125
00:08:14,740 --> 00:08:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make it up to you later.</font>

126
00:08:16,690 --> 00:08:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

127
00:08:17,910 --> 00:08:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand.</font>

128
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, why did you do this?</font>

129
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

130
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you save me?</font>

131
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that contract...</font>

132
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want me to do?</font>

133
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a beautiful afternoon.</font>

134
00:08:35,930 --> 00:08:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's take a walk.</font>

135
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

136
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

137
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you save me?</font>

138
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I killed someone.
I should be punished.</font>

139
00:08:57,400 --> 00:09:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean saving your 
father's life from a bandit?</font>

140
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's just self-defense.</font>

141
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did what anyone would do.</font>

142
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even if you forgive my actions,</font>

143
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a witch,</font>

144
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the embodiment of the Devil.</font>

145
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The original sin cannot be erased.</font>

146
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna, this flower is for you.</font>

147
00:09:33,830 --> 00:09:34,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

148
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A citrus flower... It's beautiful.</font>

149
00:09:38,010 --> 00:09:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

150
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But did you know the citrus 
flower is highly poisonous?</font>

151
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kidding.</font>

152
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could a citrus flower be poisonous?</font>

153
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that common knowledge?</font>

154
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet when I said it was poisonous,</font>

155
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you instinctively let go of it.</font>

156
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The citrus flower is still 
the same citrus flower.</font>

157
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its essence hasn't changed.</font>

158
00:10:00,930 --> 00:10:03,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What changed is our perception of it.</font>

159
00:10:03,430 --> 00:10:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you mean it's the same with witches?</font>

160
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

161
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my opinion, a witch's 
power is like this flower.</font>

162
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both are products of nature.</font>

163
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're neither inherently good nor evil.</font>

164
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this talk of the Devil and impurity,</font>

165
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's just people's opinions.</font>

166
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since it's an opinion, 
it can be changed, right?</font>

167
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:26,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness,
your thinking is too simplistic.</font>

168
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This power... is truly terrifying.</font>

169
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mother!</font>

170
00:10:33,310 --> 00:10:35,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Church is right.</font>

171
00:10:35,690 --> 00:10:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A witch's power is the Devil's power.</font>

172
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Witches are the embodiment of the Devil.</font>

173
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This power will kill 
everyone who comes near me.</font>

174
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should execute me immediately.</font>

175
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're determined to die,
no one can stop you.</font>

176
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dying won't solve the problem, though.</font>

177
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just avoiding it.</font>

178
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your father won't change 
his attitude toward witches.</font>

179
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And everything you've 
lost won't come back.</font>

180
00:11:18,170 --> 00:11:20,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or you can choose another path,</font>

181
00:11:21,450 --> 00:11:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and create a new world with me 
where witches can live freely.</font>

182
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that world, you won't 
have to live in fear.</font>

183
00:11:33,650 --> 00:11:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't have to hide.</font>

184
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't have to hide your power 
or be ashamed of your identity.</font>

185
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead, you can choose the life you want,</font>

186
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and use your powers to benefit others.</font>

187
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my opinion, that alone could 
change this suffering world.</font>

188
00:11:47,780 --> 00:11:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like this citrus flower,</font>

189
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which symbolizes strength within hardship.</font>

190
00:11:53,290 --> 00:11:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That can never be the Devil's power.</font>

191
00:11:56,310 --> 00:11:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The contract I gave you</font>

192
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is a request for you to do this with me.</font>

193
00:12:04,350 --> 00:12:06,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to go back to school,</font>

194
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to read aloud with everyone 
in the classroom,</font>

195
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and to sing in the fields.</font>

196
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In future, I want to 
become like Professor Karl,</font>

197
00:12:17,310 --> 00:12:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be with children every day,</font>

198
00:12:20,370 --> 00:12:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">teaching them to read and write.</font>

199
00:12:25,570 --> 00:12:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

200
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will that day...</font>

201
00:12:32,980 --> 00:12:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">truly come?</font>

202
00:12:37,170 --> 00:12:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will.</font>

203
00:12:39,890 --> 00:12:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as we work together.</font>

204
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm willing to give it a go.</font>

205
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do I need to do?</font>

206
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, you must learn 
to control your power.</font>

207
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, this will 
be your training ground.</font>

208
00:13:19,650 --> 00:13:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must completely master this power,</font>

209
00:13:21,650 --> 00:13:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and control the temperature, 
angle, and every other aspect.</font>

210
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But don't burn your clothes again.</font>

211
00:13:34,970 --> 00:13:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or anything else, for that matter.</font>

212
00:14:59,250 --> 00:15:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Last night, I reviewed last 
year's industrial reports</font>

213
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and discovered that</font>

214
00:15:02,690 --> 00:15:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the only significant industry
in Border Town is mining.</font>

215
00:15:05,850 --> 00:15:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only does this include building stone,</font>

216
00:15:08,130 --> 00:15:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but also a substantial quantity of 
metal ores and gemstones.</font>

217
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now look at this financial statement.</font>

218
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Last year's fiscal 
revenue was nearly zero.</font>

219
00:15:16,810 --> 00:15:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only that, but trade records 
show only a few ore transactions</font>

220
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and some deals for iron goods,</font>

221
00:15:21,690 --> 00:15:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all conducted with Willow Town.</font>

222
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This meager revenue barely 
covers municipal expenses.</font>

223
00:15:27,850 --> 00:15:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of the mining output 
wasn't recorded at all.</font>

224
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's also nothing on 
daily living expenses or taxes.</font>

225
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Based on this, it seems Border Town 
has no agricultural production.</font>

226
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If everyone is engaged in mining work,</font>

227
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">how do they manage their 
daily food supply?</font>

228
00:15:42,090 --> 00:15:47,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, did you spend all night 
reviewing these reports?</font>

229
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With so many reports, you must be...</font>

230
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it took a while.</font>

231
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew far too little 
about my domain before.</font>

232
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I left everything to you,</font>

233
00:15:57,620 --> 00:16:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while I indulged in revelry all by myself.</font>

234
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. Thanks for your hard work.</font>

235
00:16:03,290 --> 00:16:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

236
00:16:04,090 --> 00:16:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, I will do what I need to do.</font>

237
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do your best to assist me.</font>

238
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will obey your orders 
and do my very best.</font>

239
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, actually, until last year,</font>

240
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all ore produced in Border Town</font>

241
00:16:20,270 --> 00:16:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was exchanged for food
with Longsong Stronghold.</font>

242
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exchanged? Wasn't it sold?</font>

243
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:35,720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}LONGSONG STRONGHOLD</font>

244
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the eyes of Longsong Stronghold,</font>

245
00:16:26,990 --> 00:16:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Border Town is nothing more 
than their property.</font>

246
00:16:29,650 --> 00:16:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They provide meager rations 
to keep the workers going.</font>

247
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:35,720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}BORDER TOWN</font>

248
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can hardly call 
them a trading partner.</font>

249
00:16:36,610 --> 00:16:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before your arrival,</font>

250
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the original lord of 
Border Town, Baron Boris,</font>

251
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">always obeyed the Stronghold's orders,</font>

252
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">handing over all ores to them
in exchange for meager rations.</font>

253
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron Boris... I remember him.</font>

254
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was a weirdo.</font>

255
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:55,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came and seized his territory.</font>

256
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's understandable that he dislikes me.</font>

257
00:16:57,930 --> 00:16:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But logically speaking,</font>

258
00:16:59,430 --> 00:17:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">since Border Town was his domain,</font>

259
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even if it was for his own benefit,</font>

260
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he should have wanted to 
trade the ores fairly, right?</font>

261
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These ores are valuable.</font>

262
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although Boris and his knights, 
along with several other nobles,</font>

263
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are nominally lords of Border Town,</font>

264
00:17:15,780 --> 00:17:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they actually own property 
in Longsong Stronghold.</font>

265
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their personal interests and businesses 
are tied to Longsong Stronghold.</font>

266
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They never intended to manage Border Town,</font>

267
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and are merely acting as 
overseers for the Stronghold.</font>

268
00:17:29,410 --> 00:17:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They couldn't care less about it.</font>

269
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're happy as long as they do their 
job and exchange ores for food.</font>

270
00:17:35,630 --> 00:17:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Stronghold also gives 
them a share of the profits.</font>

271
00:17:38,810 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an exaggeration 
to call it an exchange.</font>

272
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how much ore we give them,</font>

273
00:17:44,070 --> 00:17:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the food they give us 
barely keeps us alive.</font>

274
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The town's daily expenses still depend 
on that meager trade with Willow Town.</font>

275
00:17:51,860 --> 00:17:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Stronghold doesn't 
contribute a single penny.</font>

276
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't carry on like this.</font>

277
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cease all exchanges with 
the Stronghold immediately.</font>

278
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about our future food supply?</font>

279
00:18:04,850 --> 00:18:07,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}BORDER TOWN</font>

280
00:18:05,300 --> 00:18:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Border Town will start genuine trade.</font>

281
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:10,220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}LONGSONG STRONGHOLD</font>

282
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sell all the ore already loaded onto 
ships to Willow Town for currency,</font>

283
00:18:10,220 --> 00:18:13,600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}WILLOW TOWN</font>

284
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then buy food directly there.</font>

285
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what if Willow Town doesn't buy?</font>

286
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, they've never handled 
such a large ore transaction before.</font>

287
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can sell to them at 
half the market price.</font>

288
00:18:24,300 --> 00:18:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With such a large profit, 
they won't refuse.</font>

289
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Half?</font>

290
00:18:27,810 --> 00:18:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. We will immediately 
obtain substantial start-up capital</font>

291
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and quickly dominate the market.</font>

292
00:18:33,100 --> 00:18:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But at such a low price...</font>

293
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the future?</font>

294
00:18:37,210 --> 00:18:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the future, we don't necessarily 
have to sell to Willow Town.</font>

295
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this map, Barov.</font>

296
00:18:40,190 --> 00:18:42,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}BORDER TOWN</font>

297
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Border Town is the source 
of the Redwater River,</font>

298
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:44,310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}LONGSONG STRONGHOLD</font>

299
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which flows through the entire kingdom.</font>

300
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:46,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}WILLOW TOWN</font>

301
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once we have enough ships, 
we won't be limited to Willow Town.</font>

302
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:48,230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}REDWATER CITY</font>

303
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can navigate the Redwater River 
and trade with the entire kingdom.</font>

304
00:18:50,690 --> 00:18:52,770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}SILVER CITY</font>

305
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Redwater River will become 
Border Town's Silk Road.</font>

306
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:56,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ROYAL CAPITAL OF GRAYCASTLE</font>

307
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Your Highness,</font>

308
00:18:59,770 --> 00:19:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Border Town doesn't produce silk.</font>

309
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was just an analogy.</font>

310
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, we can use the Redwater River</font>

311
00:19:07,530 --> 00:19:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and comprehensively expand 
our trading partners.</font>

312
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, although 
expanding trade is great,</font>

313
00:19:16,110 --> 00:19:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">doing so would be like snatching food
from the Stronghold's mouth.</font>

314
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, they probably 
won't take us in during winter.</font>

315
00:19:25,190 --> 00:19:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take us in? Why do we need to 
spend winter in the Stronghold?</font>

316
00:19:28,320 --> 00:19:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, how could you forget this?</font>

317
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Winter brings the Months of Demons!</font>

318
00:19:34,930 --> 00:19:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Months of Demons?</font>

319
00:19:36,430 --> 00:19:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After the first snowfall each winter,</font>

320
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:42,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Gates of Hell open within 
the Dragonspine Mountain.</font>

321
00:19:42,660 --> 00:19:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Animals from the Misty Forest 
west of Border Town,</font>

322
00:19:45,670 --> 00:19:47,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">corrupted by demonic power,</font>

323
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will transform into ferocious 
and bloodthirsty demon beasts.</font>

324
00:19:51,120 --> 00:19:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They surge forth in hordes from the 
Misty Forest, attacking eastward,</font>

325
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">leaving devastation in their wake.</font>

326
00:19:57,580 --> 00:20:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Border Town has no walls.</font>

327
00:20:00,060 --> 00:20:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We cannot withstand the beasts' onslaught.</font>

328
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, every winter, 
the residents of Border Town</font>

329
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">must evacuate to 
Longsong Stronghold for refuge.</font>

330
00:20:08,910 --> 00:20:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only the Stronghold's towering 
walls and elite knights</font>

331
00:20:12,610 --> 00:20:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can withstand the demon beasts' onslaught.</font>

332
00:20:15,050 --> 00:20:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only after the beasts have 
retreated the following spring</font>

333
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can the people return to Border Town.</font>

334
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every winter, the residents 
of Border Town must migrate.</font>

335
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In other words, without solving 
the demon beast problem,</i></font>

336
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it's impossible to establish a foothold 
in Border Town, develop trade,</i></font>

337
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>resist the Stronghold,</i></font>

338
00:20:33,810 --> 00:20:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>or even think about the ambition 
of claiming the throne.</i></font>

339
00:20:36,870 --> 00:20:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Summon Carter.</font>

340
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, I've brought 
the men you requested.</font>

341
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of them have lived in 
Border Town for over five years,</font>

342
00:20:42,970 --> 00:20:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have experienced the Months of Demons.</font>

343
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These two are the patrol 
captains of Border Town.</font>

344
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:49,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every year, they light the beacon fires 
during the Months of Demons.</font>

345
00:20:49,840 --> 00:20:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This hunter claims to have 
fought the demon beasts</font>

346
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and personally killed two.</font>

347
00:20:57,890 --> 00:21:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the procedure for 
lighting the beacon fires?</font>

348
00:21:00,420 --> 00:21:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Y-Yes...</font>

349
00:21:02,090 --> 00:21:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Your... Your H-Highness...</font>

350
00:21:06,210 --> 00:21:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the demon beasts 
cross the Misty Forest,</font>

351
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'd go and...</font>

352
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, don't be nervous. Relax.</font>

353
00:21:15,990 --> 00:21:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes...</font>

354
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You speak for him.</font>

355
00:21:18,730 --> 00:21:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

356
00:21:20,870 --> 00:21:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our patrol's outpost is located on
the Dragonspine Mountain's southern slope.</font>

357
00:21:24,020 --> 00:21:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Misty Forest lies at 
the foot of the mountain.</font>

358
00:21:25,810 --> 00:21:29,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every late fall, our patrol closely 
monitors the Misty Forest.</font>

359
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we spot any trace of demon beasts,
we immediately light the beacon fires.</font>

360
00:21:32,390 --> 00:21:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we take a fast boat along the 
Redwater River and meet at the Stronghold.</font>

361
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fast boat? Wouldn't you get attacked 
by demon beasts in the water?</font>

362
00:21:39,740 --> 00:21:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, the Redwater River 
has fierce currents and is very deep.</font>

363
00:21:43,270 --> 00:21:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In all these years, we've never recorded 
a single case of a demon beast crossing it.</font>

364
00:21:47,180 --> 00:21:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Dragonspine Mountain's beacon towers 
are very close to the river bank.</font>

365
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're agile and usually aren't in danger.</font>

366
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long are the Months of Demons?</font>

367
00:21:56,650 --> 00:21:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roughly two to three months.</font>

368
00:21:59,140 --> 00:22:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once it starts snowing in 
Border Town, it won't stop.</font>

369
00:22:01,350 --> 00:22:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The snow only melts 
when the sky clears up again.</font>

370
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Months of Demons only 
end when the snow melts.</font>

371
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The longest Months of Demons 
I experienced was two years ago.</font>

372
00:22:10,730 --> 00:22:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one lasted nearly four months.</font>

373
00:22:12,910 --> 00:22:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Due to starvation,</font>

374
00:22:14,290 --> 00:22:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">many didn't survive that winter.</font>

375
00:22:16,630 --> 00:22:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Starvation? But weren't you 
in Longsong Stronghold?</font>

376
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Stronghold...</font>

377
00:22:22,870 --> 00:22:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They provide food based on 
the amount of ore we give.</font>

378
00:22:25,850 --> 00:22:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we ration carefully, 
it lasts three months at most.</font>

379
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Food for a fourth month
wouldn't be provided</font>

380
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">until another batch of ore arrived.</font>

381
00:22:33,150 --> 00:22:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the Months of Demons 
hadn't passed yet.</font>

382
00:22:35,410 --> 00:22:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There was no way we could return 
to Border Town to mine ore.</font>

383
00:22:38,850 --> 00:22:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that final month,</font>

384
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they watched us starve to death 
inside Longsong Stronghold.</font>

385
00:22:54,010 --> 00:22:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you once killed two demon beasts.</font>

386
00:22:58,130 --> 00:23:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

387
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I killed a boar-type and a wolf-type.</font>

388
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boar-type? Wolf-type?</font>

389
00:23:05,810 --> 00:23:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

390
00:23:07,020 --> 00:23:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demon beasts are mutated wild animals.</font>

391
00:23:10,100 --> 00:23:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mutation amplifies some 
of their primal instincts.</font>

392
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fiercer the animal before mutation,</font>

393
00:23:14,410 --> 00:23:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the more formidable it becomes afterward.</font>

394
00:23:16,750 --> 00:23:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, the boar-type has 
incredibly tough hide on its back.</font>

395
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even crossbows struggle to 
pierce it from 50 meters away.</font>

396
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wolf-type can run extremely fast.</font>

397
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To kill one, you have 
to set traps in advance.</font>

398
00:23:28,060 --> 00:23:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The strong get stronger, 
the fast get faster.</font>

399
00:23:29,830 --> 00:23:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're still just animals, right?</font>

400
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's correct,</font>

401
00:23:33,170 --> 00:23:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they're not the most terrifying foes.</font>

402
00:23:35,280 --> 00:23:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The truly terrifying ones are the hybrids.</font>

403
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:40,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are the incarnations of demons.</font>

404
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only Hell could create 
such monstrous beasts.</font>

405
00:23:43,670 --> 00:23:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hybrids...</font>

406
00:23:45,570 --> 00:23:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you seen one?</font>

407
00:23:47,010 --> 00:23:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has the strength of a lion,</font>

408
00:23:49,020 --> 00:23:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">bears the wings of an eagle,</font>

409
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and can fly short distances.</font>

410
00:23:52,490 --> 00:23:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It knows where you are.</font>

411
00:23:54,130 --> 00:23:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how well you hide,</font>

412
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it can find you with its keen 
sense of smell and toy with you.</font>

413
00:23:59,170 --> 00:24:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's as if it takes pleasure 
in its prey's death throes.</font>

414
00:24:04,020 --> 00:24:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There aren't many of 
these monsters, right?</font>

415
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

416
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are only two or three 
in each Months of Demons.</font>

417
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fortunately, even though they have wings,</font>

418
00:24:12,150 --> 00:24:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they can only glide at low altitudes.</font>

419
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, even the walls</font>

420
00:24:15,630 --> 00:24:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of Longsong Stronghold 
wouldn't hold them back.</font>

421
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name? 
Why are you keeping your head down?</font>

422
00:24:24,540 --> 00:24:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raise your head.</font>

423
00:24:27,280 --> 00:24:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's from the Mojin Clan.</font>

424
00:24:28,530 --> 00:24:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Sand person in exile, Your Highness.</font>

425
00:24:31,410 --> 00:24:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sand person?</font>

426
00:24:33,520 --> 00:24:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter who you are,</font>

427
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as long as you're in 
Border Town, you're my people.</font>

428
00:24:37,320 --> 00:24:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raise your head.</font>

429
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me your name.</font>

430
00:24:41,150 --> 00:24:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is... Iron Axe.</font>

431
00:24:43,250 --> 00:24:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done, Iron Axe.</font>

432
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your courage will be rewarded.</font>

433
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, thanks to the rest of you 
for your service and intelligence.</font>

434
00:24:49,910 --> 00:24:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Each of you will receive 
ten silver royals as reward.</font>

435
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may leave.</font>

436
00:24:53,590 --> 00:24:56,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Thank you, Your Highness.</font>

437
00:25:01,970 --> 00:25:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter.</font>

438
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

439
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me.</font>

440
00:25:05,530 --> 00:25:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

441
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Every winter, upon the first sighting 
of traces of demonic beasts,</i></font>

442
00:25:29,090 --> 00:25:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the patrols light the beacon tower.</i></font>

443
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then, they rush down the mountain</i></font>

444
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to the nearest bank of the Redwater River.</i></font>

445
00:25:48,420 --> 00:25:52,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter, roughly how far would you say 
it is from here to the river bank?</font>

446
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roughly...</font>

447
00:25:55,180 --> 00:25:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">around 2000 feet.</font>

448
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, forgive my directness,</font>

449
00:26:01,290 --> 00:26:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but why are you investigating this?</font>

450
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me... you plan to 
spend the winter in Border Town?</font>

451
00:26:07,950 --> 00:26:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

452
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only will I not leave,</font>

453
00:26:10,990 --> 00:26:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but neither will the 2000 
residents of Border Town.</font>

454
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone will spend the winter here.</font>

455
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This... This is crazy, Your Highness!</font>

456
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only have a few dozen guards.</font>

457
00:26:20,090 --> 00:26:22,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can we defend against 
the demon beasts' onslaught?</font>

458
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your castle can't fit over 2000 
residents from Border Town!</font>

459
00:26:25,530 --> 00:26:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only Longsong Stronghold 
can hold all of us</font>

460
00:26:28,190 --> 00:26:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and defend against the 
invasion of the demon beasts.</font>

461
00:26:30,210 --> 00:26:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough, Carter.</font>

462
00:26:31,570 --> 00:26:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I don't want to die here,</font>

463
00:26:33,530 --> 00:26:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">nor will I abandon my people.</font>

464
00:26:35,970 --> 00:26:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is our battlefield.</font>

465
00:26:38,230 --> 00:26:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will stand our ground here.</font>

466
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will crush the beasts 
and defend Border Town.</font>

467
00:26:42,890 --> 00:26:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you saying?</font>

468
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, we will defend against 
the demon beasts here.</font>

469
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will build the strongest wall here.</font>

470
00:26:56,060 --> 00:26:59,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Translator: Henry Lin
Timer: Henry Lin
